          {
            "title": "Question: As many as we'd like",
            "id": 78079,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A indentação de <code>print(\"My favorite color!\")</code> é diferente no primeiro bloco <code>if</code> em comparação com o segundo.</p><p>Este código gera um <code>IndentationError</code>. Qual bloco <code>if</code> o causa?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;red&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" color == \" /><text value=\"&quot;blue&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Blue is awesome!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;My favorite color!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" color == \" /><text value=\"&quot;green&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Green is awesome!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;My favorite color!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"  File &quot;/home/code/file.py&quot;, line 4\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(&quot;My favorite color!&quot;)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"                               ^\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"IndentationError: unindent does not match any outer indentation level\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"\" /></content></output></code><selection multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">O bloco <code>\"blue\"</code>, como a indentação do segundo <code>print()</code> é diferente tanto dos outros <code>print()</code> quanto do <code>if</code>, então o computador não entende a que ele pertence</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">O bloco <code>\"green\"</code>, como o segundo <code>print()</code>, está indentado como a palavra-chave <code>if</code></item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\">Ambos</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">O bloco <code>\"blue\"</code>, como a indentação do segundo <code>print()</code> é diferente tanto dos outros <code>print()</code> quanto do <code>if</code>, então o computador não entende a que ele pertence.</p></body></html>"
